title: Private patio and/or balcony, Gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops
posting_body: Establish new roots in beautiful Duvall, where life is a little greener and there are trails around every corner.
Recognized as the best suburb in the Seattle area by <URL>, Duvall offers that small town feel but with convenient proximity to Seattle, Redmond and Bellevue.
Choose from two-, three- four and five-bedroom townhome options, all of which provide plenty of space, but with none of the stresses of homeownership.
We'll coordinate landscaping and maintenance for you so you have your weekends back to do what you enjoy more!
Other perks like outdoor fitness equipment and direct access to the Snoqualmie Valley Trail are available to all Duvall Village residents.
This is a 4 Bedroom, 3.5 Bath, approximately 2133 Sq.
- Full sized, side-by-side washer and dryer
- Double sink vanity in master bathrooms
- Designer vinyl flooring with carpeted bedrooms
- Large kitchen islands with breakfast bar seating *Kitchen pantry storage*
- Modern LED lighting Loft, den, home office or bonus room*
- Bellevue and Issaquah are a mere 35-minute commute
- Redmond employers and activities are only 25 minutes away by car
- Lawn care and landscaping services provided
- Advanced fiber internet access through Ziply, Frontier and Wave
- Pet-friendly with multiple walking trails on-site and nearby
- Beautiful natural setting with multiple wetlands and green spaces
- Safeway, Starbucks & many everyday services nearby
- Adjacent to the upcoming Duvall Cultural & Performing Arts Center
- Direct access to the Snoqualmie Valley Trail for hiking or biking
- Ski adventures at Stevens Pass just over an hour away
- Hikes like Cherry Falls, Trillium Trail and Ring Hill Forest Trail are nearby
- Modern Craftsman and Farmhouse design options
- Big Rock Park and Duvall Park are a very short walk away
- Downtown Duvall shops, cafés, services and schools are less than a 5-minute drive
- Multiple parks and walking trails are available across the area
